        "lang": "en",
        "text": "“I the Lord do not change. So you, the descendants of Jacob, are not destroyed."
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "“I am the Lord, and I do not change. That is why you descendants of Jacob are not already destroyed."
      }
